        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar a = parseFloat(age);\nvar b = parseFloat(world);\nvar c = parseFloat(orient);\nvar d = parseFloat(nursing);\n\nvar score = a + b + c + d; \n\nvar risk1;\n\nif (score == 0) {\n\trisk1 = '2';\n}\nelse if (score == 1) { \n\trisk1 = '4';\n}\nelse if (score == 2) { \n\trisk1 = '14';\n}\nelse if (score == 3) { \n\trisk1 = '20';\n}\nelse if (score == 4) { \n\trisk1 = '64';\n}\n\n//results\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: risk1 + '% risk of delirium'\n});\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'Score',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'AWOL Score'   \n    });\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'risk1',\n    value: risk1, \n    value_text: '%',\n    message: 'Risk of delirium during hospitalization'\n});\n",
